<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q25_v3" title="Q25_v3" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceA</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Primero desarrolla el producto 
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mo>-</m:mo>
          <m:mn>4</m:mn>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mi>t</m:mi>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mn>5</m:mn>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>.
      Luego suma 2t al resultado obtenido. 
      ¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones es equivalente al resultado final?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>-</m:mo>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mi>t</m:mi>
            <m:mo>-</m:mo>
            <m:mn>20</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Al desarrollar, −4(t + 5) = −4t − 20. Luego, al sumar 2t, se obtiene −4t − 20 + 2t = −2t − 20. Esa expresión coincide exactamente con la alternativa.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>-</m:mo>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mi>t</m:mi>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>20</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al desarrollar, −4(t + 5) = −4t − 20, porque −4 × 5 = −20. Luego, al sumar 2t, resulta −4t − 20 + 2t = −2t − 20. El término independiente final es −20, no +20.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>-</m:mo>
            <m:mn>6</m:mn>
            <m:mi>t</m:mi>
            <m:mo>-</m:mo>
            <m:mn>20</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al desarrollar, −4(t + 5) = −4t − 20. Después se suma 2t, de modo que los términos semejantes quedan −4t + 2t = −2t. Por eso el resultado final es −2t − 20, no −6t − 20.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>-</m:mo>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mi>t</m:mi>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>5</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al desarrollar, −4(t + 5) = −4t − 20. Luego, al sumar 2t, queda −4t − 20 + 2t = −2t − 20. El término independiente debe ser −20, porque proviene de −4 × 5, no +5.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Desarrollar el producto</strong></p>
            <p>Se distribuye el <m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> en cada término del paréntesis:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>t</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>t</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>20</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Esto ocurre porque:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>t</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>t</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
              y
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>20</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Sumar 2t al resultado obtenido</strong></p>
            <p>Ahora se suma <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math> a la expresión anterior:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>t</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>20</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>t</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Reducir términos semejantes</strong></p>
            <p>Se agrupan los términos con <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>t</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>t</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>t</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>t</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>t</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>20</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>t</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>t</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>20</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión equivalente al resultado final es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  <m:mi>t</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>-</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>20</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, la alternativa correcta es <strong>A</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>